T02TD2235E:112a-1: aa pra sa ha pra ka sa n'a ma /
T02TD2235E:112a-3: rab tu mi gnas pa gsal bar ston pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD2235E:112a-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2235E:112a-5: shes pa rab tu mi gnas pa //
T02TD2235E:112b-0: @112b sangs rgyas pha nor thams cad 'dod //
T02TD2235E:112b-2: gang tshe sems can don byed na'o //
T02TD2235E:112b-3: gang phyir gzhan sel sgrub las skyes //
T02TD2235E:112b-4: de ni rtag dang chad la gnas //
T02TD2235E:112b-5: rtag tu ma skyes mi 'gag nyid //
T02TD2235E:112b-6: skye dang 'gag pa byol song tshig / gal te rang rig tshad ma ni //
T02TD2235E:112b-7: rig de sems can 'dod ma yin //
T02TD2235E:112b-8: snang ba thams cad spang ba'i phyir //
T02TD2235E:112b-9: sems can bden pa ma yin no //
T02TD2235E:112b-10: rjes la sems can 'dod ce na //
T02TD2235E:112b-11: de tshe sems can rdzas yod min //
T02TD2235E:112b-12: dam bcas gcod pa gnod pa'i don //
T02TD2235E:112b-13: rjes su rtag pa zhes brjod do //
T02TD2235E:112b-14: dngos gzhi la yang rig pa yod //
T02TD2235E:112b-15: rjes la de ltar snang ba'i phyir //
T02TD2235E:112b-16: dang po mi rtog par 'gyur gyis //
T02TD2235E:112b-19: sems ni gnas pa yod ma yin //
T02TD2235E:112b-20: des na de dag med par ni //
T02TD2235E:112b-22: / chos rnams kyi ni skye ba nyid //
T02TD2235E:112b-23: rang nyid gnyug ma bsam mi khyab //
T02TD2235E:112b-24: de nyid stong pa nyid ces brjod //
T02TD2235E:112b-25: chad pa'i rjes 'gro ma yin no //
T02TD2235E:112b-26: rab tu mi gnas sa bon las //
T02TD2235E:112b-28: skyob pa de nyid dam pa ste //
T02TD2235E:112b-29: bcos ma'i bcos ma de bzhin no //
T02TD2235E:112b-30: de bzhin bsam gtan yod med ces //
T02TD2235E:112b-31: chags med spyod la brjod du med //
T02TD2235E:112b-32: gang phyir rten nas 'byung ba rnams //
T02TD2235E:112b-33: nyams myong ji bzhin rtag tu skye //
T02TD2235E:112b-34: rten nas 'byung ba gang dang gang //
T02TD2235E:112b-35: de de gnyis med sna tshogs sems //
T02TD2235E:112b-36: stong dang sna tshogs sems dbye bas //
T02TD2235E:112b-37: chos dang longs spyod sprul pa nyid //
T02TD2235E:112b-38: bdag gis mi gnas brjod pa las //
T02TD2235E:112b-39: bde ba bsgags pa gang yod des //
T02TD2235E:112b-40: nye bar spyod pa thams cad dang //
T02TD2235E:112b-41: 'gro rnams mi gnas thob par shog / rab tu mi gnas pa gsal bar bstan pa /
T02TD2235E:112b-42: slob dpon gnyis med rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
